  <summary date="2020-04-23T21:17:10Z" status="Introduced in House">State Operations Stabilization (SOS) Act

This bill authorizes a state, tribal government, or unit of local government to use funds made available under the Coronavirus Relief Fund to reduce a budget deficit of such government that occurred due to a loss of revenue related to the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) public health emergency.</summary>
